#summary This is the Example 2

= Search all human proteins which are linked to one of the Ontologies in the Ontology List =

On this example the [DesktopTool Desktop Tool] [SearchTab Search Tab], [SQLEditor SQL Editor Tab] and the [JavaAPI Java API] will be used to search all human proteins which are linked to one of the Ontologies in the Ontology List.

The ontology list will be integrated by the glycoprotein metabolic process (GO:0009100) and the glycoprotein biosynthetic process (GO:0009101).

Follow the next links to view the solution to this question:

 * [Ex2SearchTab Search Tab]
 * [Ex2SQLEditor SQL Editor Tab]
 * [Ex2JavaAPI Java API]
